org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy
Class AeDeploymentSummary

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.deploy.AeDeploymentSummary
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeDeploymentSummary, java.io.Serializable
public class AeDeploymentSummary
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAeDeploymentSummary, java.io.Serializable

This class contains all information about the deployment of a single BPR file. Each BPR may have multiple deployment units. The result of the deployment of each unit will exist in a list.
